Instruction template for a button template (text with
buttons). 1 button minimum, 3 max? (check this). Buttons
can be a combination of web_url or postback. Payload for a
postback is the instruction that would be to come back from
the agent, NOT the message request to the agent.
<!--==============================-->

<response>
    <button_template>
        <text>__messageText</text>
        <buttons>
            <type>web_url</type>
            <url>__urlOnClick</url>
            <title>__btn1Text</title>
        </buttons>
        <buttons>
            <type>postback</type>
            <title>__btn2Text</title>
            <payload>__instructionOnClick</payload>
        </buttons>
    </button_template>
</response>